        .col-md-6
          .entry-content.pt-10
            %a.btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-primary{:href => "https://www.meetup.com/livinginspace/", :target => "_blank"} Join our Meetup Group
            %p.mt-10{:style => "text-align: left;"}
              We collaborate with 
              %strong>
                %a{:href => "http://www.innovatepasadena.org", :target => "_blank"}Innovate Pasadena
              to produce an ongoing series of meetups called 
              %em>
                %strong> Living In Space
                \.
                %strong  
              These events encourage the cross-pollination of ideas amongst scientists, engineers, artists and thinkers that are interested in all aspects of becoming a spacefaring civilization. We present challenges that stem from both socio-economical and technological perspectives, reaching out to experts from both industry and academia to inform the community about their latest work. Meetups are highly interactive and engage the audience through “brainstorming jams” that are both fun and thought-provoking.
            .sponsor.mt-30 Sponsors
